## ğŸ“¦ Quickstart

```python
from corrpy import Corrpy

corrpy = Corrpy()
corrpy.getTotalCorrRelation(df)
```

âœ… Analyze correlation across features  
âœ… Get trends + easy-to-read interpretations  
âœ… Go deeper with AI explanations (optional)

